snippet.title: Starlink Metaverse - Space Master FULL SHOW
snippet.description:
Starlink Metaverse FULL SHOW featuring Space Master in the STARL Hub Arena.

The first Metaverse created in Unreal Engine 5 on the Ethereum blockchain.

A decentralized community built space themed metaverse containing live music and events, an entire space MMO from the creators of Lego Universe and Jumpgate, living modules, arcade, meditation center, NFT marketplace, and endless creative expansion from our community, artists, and developers.

https://starlproject.com

https://twitter.com/StarLinkETH

https://t.me/STARLinkofficial

https://starl-docs.gitbook.io/starl-metaverse-documentation

Warp Nexus demo is available NOW:
https://warpnexus-client.s3.amazonaws.com/STARLMetaverse.exe
